replies.bodyText:
As stated in ASREGS
// If variables are not defined, only get variables and registers used by STORE and POPR
// to avoid global varaibles.

If a variable is only used by a LOAD, this must not be converted to a register because it is most certainly a global variable. Converting it to a register will only break the code.
